mainText:
I have been an Apple fan since 1984. Watching Steve's rise, fall and greater rise was wondrous. Even Steve's failures were simply too far ahead of their time. His attention to detail, elegance, quality and the aesthetic have been greatly appreciated.

It is with great sadness and grief that we mark Steve's passing. I offer my sincere condolences to Steve's family and friends.

The world has lost a visionary genius.&nbsp;
